iSometimes, modifying a single file can corrupt the Android system,		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ipreventing it from booting. The typical solution is to reflash the		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iROM, but this results in data loss and erases all previous system		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
imodifications.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
